    "To eliminate the effects of different scales, the normalized root mean square error (RMSE), the normalized mean absolute error (MAE), and the coefficient of determination (R 2) are introduced as metrics to show the accuracy of the prediction results in this experiment.",
    "A smaller RMSE and MAE of the model and a larger i R 2 indicate that the model is better at forecasting.",
